'''Dr. Oslow''' is a doctor for the Seattle Seahawks.

==History==
Dr. Oslow came to the hospital with [[Tom Kates]] when he was injured during a game. He described Tom's injuries and said that Tom got high-lowed by a few of the other team's quarterbacks and immediately went unconcious.

==Career==
He is the team doctor for the Seattle Seahawks.
